SUMMARY:Fundamental Designs in Adobe
LOCATION:120 W Gasparilla Plaza Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:This hands-on digital design course introduces students to the
  foundational elements and principles of design through Adobe Illustrator\
 , using a reverse-engineering approach that demystifies complex visual com
 positions. Modular patterns and Sacred Geometry are discussed as optional 
 approaches. Rather than building from simple to complex\, students will be
 gin by observing sophisticated designs and deconstructing them into their 
 fundamental componentsrevealing that inspiring\, thought-provoking artwork
  is ultimately the result of basic elements thoughtfully combined. Thursda
 ys\, May 7  Jun 11  6:009:00 PM (6 classes) Ages 18  Beginner Level \n\nPe
 rmalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/188681
