SUMMARY:Divos: Live In Concert
LOCATION:1731 East 7th Avenue Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:Our Divas dazzled you last year. Now\, Its the boys turn! Insp
 ired by VH1 - prepare to be dazzled as four powerhouse male vocalists jour
 ney through the iconic history of musics most influential fellas...told th
 rough a humorous\, if not quite factual lens. Featuring songs by renowned 
 artists like Frank Sinatra\, Elvis Presley\, Elton John\, Michael Jackson\
 , and even todays new generation of popstars\, this concert-style event wi
 ll channel the spirit and power of the legendary music that shaped the sou
 ndtrack of our lives. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/189391
