SUMMARY:Mother039\\\;s Day Brunch at Rusty Pelican Tampa
LOCATION:2425 N Rocky Point Drive Tampa \, FL 33607 United States
DESCRIPTION:Treat Mom to a truly special experience at Rusty Pelican Tampa
  with a bayfront Mothers Day three-course chefs brunch. Gather around fami
 ly-style shareable starters and a fan-favorite raw bar filled with fresh c
 oastal delicacies\, then savor elevated takes on classic brunch favorites 
 for the main course\, like indulgent French Toast\, Hot Honey Fried Chicke
 n and Waffles\, and Lobster Benedict. Finish the meal with decadent desser
 ts made to be shared around the table\, all with breathtaking views of Tam
 pa Bay as the backdrop. Elevate your brunch experience with mix-and-match 
 bottomless mimosas in unique bubbly flavors like watermelon and lime\, cuc
 umber and mint\, mango and Tajn\, and the classic orange. Mothers Day Brun
 ch at Rusty Pelican Tampa is 105 for adults and 35 for children. Bottomles
 s mimosas can be added for 30 per person \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.
 gov/node/189066
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/189066
END:VEVENT
