SUMMARY:Webinar: Goal Setting and Motivation
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Goal setting and motivation play a critical role in mental hea
 lth and emotional well-being. This seminar explores how clear\, realistic 
 goals can reduce stress\, increase self-efficacy\, and improve mood\, whil
 e unhelpful goal patterns can contribute to distress. Learn strategies for
  setting healthy goals\, maintaining motivation\, and supporting mental we
 llness in both personal and professional life. Presented by Bay Care and U
 HC Onsite Nurse Liaison. This webinar does count toward your wellness ince
 ntive benefit - 100  quarter. Registration : 5.20.26 Goal Setting and Moti
 vation (https:events.teams.microsoft.comeventb30dae4f-6f0f-492b-bb40-a8d74
 4e2dc56db05faca-c82a-4b9d-b9c5-0f64b6755421) \n\nPermalink: https://www.ta
 mpa.gov/node/185296
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/185296
END:VEVENT
