SUMMARY:Fueled by Hope in Tampa Bay Vision Dinner
LOCATION:2010 N Avenida Republica de Cuba Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:Right now\, there are over 570\,000 military-connected youth a
 round the globe. Over 10\,000 of them live here in the Tampa Bay area. Due
  to constant change\, moving every 1-3 years\, and parental deployments\, 
 they are one of the most OVERLOOKED and UNSEEN groups of teenagers in the 
 world. FUELED BY HOPE IN TAMPA BAY is a powerful evening dedicated to supp
 orting Youth For Christ Military and our mission to reach these students w
 ith the HOPE of Christ. This special event features a complimentary dinner
 \, meaningful program and inspiring stories from military youth and their 
 families. You will have an opportunity to join us in supporting them durin
 g these unpredictable times...because THEY SERVE TOO. You are warmly invit
 ed to join us in making sure these incredible youth are SEEN\, HEARD\, and
  LOVED. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/189971
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/189971
END:VEVENT
