 t poetry\, focusing on negative space and transforming the meaning of exis
 ting materials. Materials will include newspapers\, magazines\, books and 
 Sharpie markers. This workshop is inspired by Jun Kanekos Silence Before S
 ound exhibition. Ages 16  Beginner Level \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.
