SUMMARY:BAPS Charities WalkRun 2026
LOCATION:4810 N Himes Ave Tampa \, FL 33614 United States
DESCRIPTION:Driven by our motto\, The Spirit of Service\, the BAPS Chariti
 es WalkRun is an annual event that has raised vital funds for over 20 year
 s for: BAPS Charities: Funding our five key areas: Health Awareness\, Educ
 ational Services\, Humanitarian Relief\, Environmental Protection\, and Co
 mmunity Empowerment 2026 National Beneficiary: BAPS Charities 90 Local Ben
 eficiaries: Including first responders\, educational institutions\, food b
 anks\, and healthcare institutions 2026 Local Beneficiary: The Childrens C
 ancer Center This event is more than just a walk - its a platform to unite
  for the greater good\, embrace a healthier lifestyle\, and find joy in se
 rving others. We hope you will join us\, one step at a time! \n\nPermalink
 : https://www.tampa.gov/node/189941
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/189941
END:VEVENT
