SUMMARY:BayCare Presents - PTSD Matters: Raising Awareness and Building Su
 pport
LOCATION:Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD) affects millions of indi
 vidualsyet it often remains misunderstood and stigmatized. Well explore th
 e signs and symptoms\, break down common misconceptions\, and discuss prac
 tical strategies for fostering empathy\, compassion and resilience. Click 
