SUMMARY:City of Tampa Annual Juneteenth Flag Raising Ceremony and Wellness
  Fair
LOCATION:2555 East Hanna Avenue Tampa \, FL 33610 United States
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we celebrate community\, culture and freedom at the
  Annual Juneteenth Flag Raising Ceremony and Wellness Fair in partnership 
 with the Tampa Bay Juneteenth Coalition! This year\, we are honored to wel
 come special guest speaker Benjamin Haith\, designer of the Juneteenth Fla
 g\, who will share inspiring words and reflections during this meaningful 
 celebration. The event will take place on June 12 from 5 p.m. to 8 p.m. at
  the City Center at Hanna Avenue\, located at 2555 East Hanna Avenue. Foll
 owing the flag raising ceremony\, attendees are invited to enjoy FREE food
  (while supplies last)\, music\, community resource vendors and an excitin
 g LIVE fitness demonstration. Bring your water bottle\, tennis shoes and s
 unshades\, and come ready to connect\, celebrate and have a great time wit
 h the community! \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/190636
