 ion\, connection\, and support. We meet in person on the 3rd Wednesday of 
 each month at 11:00 am at: Holiday Inn Tampa North 3751 E. Fowler Ave Tamp
 a FL 33612 Each meeting features expert speakers sharing the latest inform
 ation about lung cancer\, along with time to connect with others who under
 stand the journey. This Months Topic: Advanced Care Planning: What Are You
 r Wishes Guest Speaker: Alicia Wlodynski\, LCSW\, APHSW-C A free lunch is 
